		<h2>Lawrencetown Beach</h2>
		<p>This popular sand and cobble beach on the Atlantic coast is noted for its surf. Ramped board walks, change house, toilets, canteen. Strong rip tides and currents are common - swimmers must exercise caution. Supervised swimming areas.</p>
